trans-unit.source: The type of an element in the controlled sequence.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列中項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: The type of the underlying container.
trans-unit.target: 基礎容器的類型。

trans-unit.source: Defines the interface of an STL/CLR [stack](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6ee96b9f-8a33-4cf7-b7e0-6535c24bdefb) object.
trans-unit.target: 定義 STL/CLR [stack](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6ee96b9f-8a33-4cf7-b7e0-6535c24bdefb) 物件的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The container adapter whose elements are to be inserted into the container.
trans-unit.target: 要將其項目插入至容器的容器配接器。

trans-unit.source: Replaces all elements in the container with the elements in the provided container.
trans-unit.target: 以所提供之容器中的項目取代容器的所有項目。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [stack::assign (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/18cc35ad-23cf-4a5a-adae-d967dc5d6980).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[stack::assign (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/18cc35ad-23cf-4a5a-adae-d967dc5d6980)。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the container contains no elements.
trans-unit.target: 判斷容器是否不含項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the container contains no elements; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果容器內沒有項目則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [stack::empty (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/30bb4ec6-e7a1-4137-99ba-0e0ebdf31baf).

trans-unit.source: Removes the last element of the container.
trans-unit.target: 移除容器的最後一個項目。

trans-unit.source: The value to be appended to the container.
trans-unit.target: 要附加至容器的值。

trans-unit.source: Appends an element to the container.
trans-unit.target: 將項目附加至容器。

trans-unit.target: 計算容器中的項目數目。
